Survey Tools gives you distance measurements between two points using Redstone Torches.
1. Place a Redstone Torch on the block you would like to &nmeasure from.
2. Using a second Redstone Torch, shift-right-click the first Redstone Torchto set your survey marker.
3. Shift-right-click another block to get a Survey Report with the distance to the first block.